OL,3,CPolice investigating cold case murder
OL,4,C33 years ago release victim's final
OL,5,Cnote
OL,7,FThe last note written by a murder
OL,8,Fvictim has been released by police
OL,9,Fhoping to trace her killer, more than
OL,10,Fthree decades after her body was found.
OL,12,FCarol Clark, from Bristol, was found
OL,13,Fstrangled in the Gloucester and
OL,14,FSharpness Canal on Sunday March 28
OL,15,F1993.
OL,17,FThe 32-year-old sex worker had last
OL,18,Fbeen seen near her home in Montpelier,
OL,19,FBristol two days earlier. She was
OL,20,Fgetting into a Volvo car around 1130pm.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
