PN,43702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1774861565
OL,3,CPolice investigating cold case murder
OL,4,C33 years ago release victim's final
OL,5,Cnote
OL,7,FThe handwritten note, to her
OL,8,Fboyfriend, was written late on Friday
OL,9,Fsaying that she would be back home by
OL,10,F2.30am on Saturday 27th March.
OL,12,FA woman matching Carol's description
OL,13,Fwas seen walking with two men along
OL,14,Fthe Berkeley bypass on the Saturday.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1774861565
OL,3,CPolice investigating cold case murder
OL,4,C33 years ago release victim's final
OL,5,Cnote
OL,7,FDet Ch Insp Wayne Usher, of
OL,8,FGloucestershire Police said, 'I am
OL,9,Fconvinced someone out there knows what
OL,10,Fhappened to Carol and we remain
OL,11,Fcommitted to doing everything we can
OL,12,Fto secure justice for her and her
OL,13,Ffamily.
OL,15,F'This weekend marks the 33rd
OL,16,Fanniversary of the day her body was
OL,17,Fdiscovered and so we wanted to use
OL,18,Fthis opportunity to once again appeal
OL,19,Ffor anyone who may have information
OL,20,Fwhich could help us.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1774861565
OL,3,CPolice investigating cold case murder
OL,4,C33 years ago release victim's final
OL,5,Cnote
OL,7,F'We strongly suspect Carol was alive
OL,8,Fall of Saturday 27 March 1993 and she
OL,9,Fwas potentially with two men.
OL,11,FDet Ch Insp Wayne Usher added: 'We
OL,12,Falso suspect Carol's body will have
OL,13,Fbeen left at Sharpness Docks in
OL,14,Fdaylight hours at a time when there
OL,15,Fwere lots of people around celebrating
OL,16,Fthe 200th anniversary of the British
OL,17,FWaterways.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1774861565
OL,3,CPolice investigating cold case murder
OL,4,C33 years ago release victim's final
OL,5,Cnote
OL,7,F'Carol was wearing distinctive
OL,8,Fclothing at the time she went missing
OL,9,Fand so we are once again asking anyone
OL,10,Fwho can recall seeing her that
OL,11,FSaturday or seeing anyone behaving
OL,12,Fsuspiciously to contact us. You could
OL,13,Fhave the final piece of the jigsaw
OL,14,Fwhich helps us catch those responsible
OL,15,Ffor her death.'
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
