PN,43706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1774861565
OL,3,CPolice investigating cold case murder
OL,4,C33 years ago release victim's final
OL,5,Cnote
OL,7,FDuring the past few years, three men
OL,8,Fhave been arrested on suspicion of
OL,9,FCarol's murder, a 69-year-old man from
OL,10,FGloucestershire; a 48-year-old man
OL,11,Ffrom Lincolnshire; and a 66-year-old
OL,12,Fman from Newcastle.
OL,14,FAfter the murder inquiry was wound
OL,15,Fdown, there have been reviews into the
OL,16,Fcase. It was reopened three years ago
OL,17,Fon the 30th anniversary and remains a
OL,18,Flive inquiry held within the Major
OL,19,FCrime Investigation Team.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
